snippet.title: Bombox: Unbox the Boom
snippet.description:
Bombox is a fast-paced casual game. Players must find and defuse the correct bomb wires before the countdown on the bomb box ends.
Welcome to the Steam Wishlisthttps://store.steampowered.com/app/2892770/Bombox/
